data.description: Peaceful, private home located at end of 21st Ct facing lake with long water views in both directions, private walkway along lake.The entry charms you with multiple shallow lagoons and waterfalls. Screened patio, open kitchen, dining and living rooms all have water views. Currently a 2/2 plus den which can be converted back to a 3 BR.The garage is a gym with extra room that can easily be converted back to garage.There is room for a pool. Kayaks & paddle boards OK.Outdoor sound system.All ages welcome to this guard gated community with security patrol.Amenities include:Clubhouse for social events & private parties.2 beautiful Pools,Gym,Game room,Indoor/Outdoor Spas,Basketball & Racquetball Courts, Childrens Playground.Trash Removal & Basic Cable included. Secure boat storage for rent onsite
